					<description><![CDATA[Singapore Design Week 2023 featured a symposium curated by renowned curator Paola Antonelli. The event delved into the future of design and &#8216;design of the future,&#8217; gathering influential minds from Singapore and around the world. The core theme, &#8216;Design as an enzyme for progress,&#8217; envisioned the future of design as if viewed through a microscope, [&#8230;]]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">
<html><body><p>Singapore Design Week 2023 featured a symposium curated by renowned curator Paola Antonelli. The event delved into the future of design and &lsquo;design of the future,&rsquo; gathering influential minds from Singapore and around the world. </p>



<p>The core theme, &lsquo;Design as an enzyme for progress,&rsquo; envisioned the future of design as if viewed through a microscope, drawing parallels with the processes of fermentation, synthesis, and mutation.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-vimeo wp-block-embed-vimeo thumb"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<div style="--width:798; --height:724;"><img decoding="async" style="--twidth:640; --theight:581;" alt="thumbnail" src="https://i.vimeocdn.com/video/1737431909-91706fd848aa222d3b67ed8d8a54bb21111c6c40d49e560bc2d571a674d725ec-d_640" fetchpriority="high"><iframe title="Design Futures Symposium &ndash; draft" src="" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture; clipboard-write" data-src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/873777229?dnt=1&amp;app_id=122963"></iframe></div>
</div></figure>



<p>The identity design embraced the metaphorical microscope, revealing a captivating cellular motif. My role was to create motion graphics that complemented this identity.</p>



